HEADWORD: Pipewort
<hw>Pipe"wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any plant of a genus (<gen>Eriocaulon</gen>) of aquatic or marsh
herbs with soft grass-like leaves.</def>⟦br⟧
